# Build game
Go to the ./build directory. If it doesn't exist, create it.
Configure the project 'cmake .. -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=C:/W/vcpkg/scripts/buildsystems/vcpkg.cmake'
Build the project 'cmake --build'

# Rebuild game
Remove ./build directory.
Create the new ./build directory.
Go to ./build directory.
Configure the project 'cmake .. -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=C:/W/vcpkg/scripts/buildsystems/vcpkg.cmake'
Build the project 'cmake --build'

# Run game
Run ./build/Debug/BrotatoGame.exe
